CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 24, 1959, pg. 2 reads: "Dedicate Homewood YMCA -Workman are shown in first photo razing the old frame house which served for many years as the Homewood-Brushton YMCA on Bennett St. near Homewood..."
TitMainTitle: Corner of old Homewood-Brushton Branch YMCA being razed, with new building on right, another version
